Package: cli-web-search
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Cross-platform CLI web search tool for AI agents
 cli-web-search is a command-line tool that provides web search capabilities
 to AI agents and CLI users. It supports multiple search API providers
 including Brave, Google CSE, DuckDuckGo, Tavily, Serper, Firecrawl,
 SerpAPI, and Bing.
 .
 Features:
  - Multiple search provider support with automatic fallback
  - JSON, Markdown, and plain text output formats
  - Result caching with configurable TTL
  - Search filtering (date range, domains, safe search)
  - Cross-platform configuration system
